Sentencas: Rare-earth doped metal oxide nanocomposites were become very unique and tend to show abundant performance in all types of fields such as electrochemical, photocatalytic, and biological.
Titulo: A simple chemical precipitation of ceria based (Sm doped-CGO) nanocomposite: structural and electrolytic behaviour for LT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Gadolinium and Samarium co-doped ceria i.e., Ce1-xGd1-yO2-delta-Ce1-xSm-yO2-delta [x = 0.2, y = 0.8] nanocomposite was synthesized by co-precipitation method for various applications.
Titulo: A simple chemical precipitation of ceria based (Sm doped-CGO) nanocomposite: structural and electrolytic behaviour for LT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The formation of fluorite cubic crystal structure was observed and functional group analysis was revealed by XRD and FTIR correspondingly.
